title: VIDEO: Which of The Muppets Would Run for President?
text:
Miss Piggy, The Muppets set visit | Photo Credits: TVGuide.com Miss Piggy, The Muppets set visit | Photo Credits: TVGuide.com VIDEO: Which of The Muppets Would Run for President? 1 / 1 Back to Gallery 
Everyone has politics on the brain -- even The Muppets . 
In an interview with Missy Piggy, Kermit the Frog and Pepe the King Prawn, TVGuide.com learned which of their puppet co-stars would be the most likely candidate to run for president. Maybe Kanye had better watch out! 
Plus: Miss Piggy gets cheeky, and Pepe reveals one of his weaknesses. Watch the video above to get the scoop. He's a spicy prawn for sure! 
The Muppets airs Tuesdays at 8/7c on ABC.
